OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772658365
OL,3,CMojtaba Khamenei: What does Iran's new
OL,4,Cleader say about the regime's
OL,5,Cintentions?
OL,7,FIran's clerical establishment did not
OL,8,Fhave to look very far to find a
OL,9,Fsuccessor to the country's Supreme
OL,10,FLeader, Ali Khamenei, who was killed
OL,11,Flast week.
OL,13,FThey chose his son, sending an
OL,14,Fimportant message at a moment of war -
OL,15,Fthe Islamic Republic intends to
OL,16,Fcontinue, not transform.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
