CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772658365
OL,3,CMojtaba Khamenei: What does Iran's new
OL,4,Cleader say about the regime's
OL,5,Cintentions?
OL,7,FIn 2009, he was reported to have taken
OL,8,Fcontrol of the militia being used to
OL,9,Fcrush a protest movement. He is also
OL,10,Fsaid to play a significant role in
OL,11,FIran's state broadcasting and
OL,12,Fpropaganda apparatus ` the same
OL,13,Fmachinery now tasked with framing his
OL,14,Ffather's death.
OL,16,FHis elevation therefore, carries both
OL,17,Fsymbolism and strategy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772658365
OL,3,CMojtaba Khamenei: What does Iran's new
OL,4,Cleader say about the regime's
OL,5,Cintentions?
OL,7,FSymbolism, because the son of the man
OL,8,Fjust killed now occupies his father's
OL,9,Fseat ` reinforcing the regime's
OL,10,Fattempt to portray Ali Khamenei as a
OL,11,Fmartyr whose legacy continues through
OL,12,Fthe system he built.
OL,14,FAnd strategy, because Mojtaba Khamenei
OL,15,Fhas long been seen as closely aligned
OL,16,Fwith Iran's most powerful security
OL,17,Finstitution, the Islamic Revolutionary
OL,18,FGuard Corps. Rumours inside Iran's
OL,19,Fpolitical establishment have for years
OL,20,Fsuggested that elements of the Guards
OL,21,Ffavoured him as a successor.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
