OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772658365
OL,3,CMojtaba Khamenei: What does Iran's new
OL,4,Cleader say about the regime's
OL,5,Cintentions?
OL,7,FIf so, the appointment represents
OL,8,Fcontinuity in the deepest sense: the
OL,9,Fclerical leadership and the security
OL,10,Fstate closing ranks.
OL,12,FUnder Article 111 of Iran's
OL,13,Fconstitution, the death of a Supreme
OL,14,FLeader triggers the creation of a
OL,15,Ftemporary leadership council, composed
OL,16,Fof the president, the head of the
OL,17,Fjudiciary and a cleric from the
OL,18,FGuardian Council, which oversees the
OL,19,Ftransition until the Assembly of
OL,20,FExperts selects a permanent successor.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
