OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772658365
OL,3,CMojtaba Khamenei: What does Iran's new
OL,4,Cleader say about the regime's
OL,5,Cintentions?
OL,7,FThis time, however, the mechanics of
OL,8,Fthat transition reflected the
OL,9,Frealities of war. Members of the
OL,10,FAssembly reportedly held portions of
OL,11,Ftheir deliberations virtually, wary
OL,12,Fthat senior clerics themselves could
OL,13,Fbecome targets of American or Israeli
OL,14,Fstrikes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
