PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772658365
OL,3,CMojtaba Khamenei: What does Iran's new
OL,4,Cleader say about the regime's
OL,5,Cintentions?
OL,7,FIn Washington, the appointment will
OL,8,Fmake Donald Trump less likely to seek
OL,9,Fan 'off ramp' - despite encouragement
OL,10,Ffrom some of his allies in the Middle
OL,11,FEast to do so. "I guess the worst case
OL,12,Fwould be we do this and somebody takes
OL,13,Fover who's as bad as the previous
OL,14,Fperson," Trump said on Tuesday.
OL,16,FThis appointment, in his view,
OL,17,Frepresents just that: hereditary
OL,18,Fcontinuity at the very top of the
OL,19,Fstate.
OL,26,@sD@POUvD@HO]
